    "text": [
        "Dear Sir or Madam,",
        "I am writing this letter to request enrollment in the \"Python Expert\" course you are offering in your college this fall. I would like to express my interest in pursuing this course.",
        "Let me explain my circumstances in more detail. I understand that the pre-requisite for joining this course is to have completed at least a basic python program course. Though my mainstream education is not in computers, I have always wanted to learn to compute. However, despite having the inclination, I could not devote my time to doing so; I suppose this could be a starting point for me.",
        "Would you be kindly interested in making an exception for me? I can attend boot-camp sessions available online to make myself acquainted with the concepts and terminologies forehand. Additionally, I can use this skill to improve my digital business operations.",
